summary: An Ordinance appropriating the sum of Eight Thousand Five Hundred Seventy-eight and 40/100 (8,578.40) Dollars or so much thereof as may be necessary from the General Fund of the City of Seattle, to pay the City's portion of the cost of the improvement of Minor Avenue et al, by paving the same, as provided for in Ordinance No. 19005, creating Local Improvement District No. 1813
